    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Biff Snodgrass is a smarmy tomb raidin’ archaeologist and your bitter rival. He hoards the ancient treasures from his adventures in a secret man cave behind a reverse escape room - a series of fiendish puzzles designed to keep you out, not in. Those ancient treasures should be in a museum!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Break into Biff’s hideout and steal the ancient treasures he's hiding to get them back where they belong!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065480/extras/9e649d49d4bc1b3e9b56ca40f6124f0c.avif?t=1733792350\" width=480 height=480 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your wits in this bite-sized puzzle adventure to figure out the gadgets and codes that guard Biff’s treasures and bypass them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\t⁃\tInnovative and irreverent puzzle design from a life time lover of the genre </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\t⁃\tLateral thinking, pen-testing fun </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\t⁃\tFully voiced larger than life characters</p>",
